{"tid":1784760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】港人乘金巴去澳門 疑於港珠澳橋人工島「被送中」","createTime":"2019-12-16T02:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T08:34:29.000Z","uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"096c1feb1935618bba9c10a02167d43c1bd85897","tid":1784760,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:08:22.000Z","msg":"有無人知搵返未？無人討論？<br />\n<br />\n陳先生形容，在爸爸失蹤的30多個小時中，感到非常驚慌失措，媽媽更情緒極不穩，「因為爸爸直情係生死未卜」。他又指，港澳兩地警方「完全幫唔到手」，互相推搪責任令他孤立無援，「淨係會講呢度唔係我哋睇，嗰度又唔係我哋管」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191214/60378529\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191214%2F60378529&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=f64d373a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191214%2F60378529&h=d24fbacf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191214/60378529</a>"},{"pid":"4c533adc74309989fb5c4632da4893d443f7da2f","tid":1784760,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"廣東省公安近日以澳門政權移交20年為由，派公安到港珠澳大橋人工島上檢查旅客，並要拍攝旅客照片。日前，一名香港男子稱，其父親在前往澳門途中失蹤。廣東省公安今日在其微博上，指香港男子鍾X明（53歲）因涉及走私手機案而被通緝，已潛逃7年，13日從前往澳門的金巴上被帶走，目前已送交內地相關部門處理。"},{"pid":"1d82a82ca934ed0f95562170d44115c024e04cfd","tid":1784760,"uid":341589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"咁都得.........CLS"}]}